      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"meaningful tapestry\" thing is just a cope. It doesn't change the fact that we're just accidental biological accidents. There is no grand design or beautiful fact to it. It's just a struggle to stay alive for no reason, and it's exhausting. It feels like fighting a losing battle against nothingness.",
